     Forestry has very few specific jobs, but most conservation or park ranger jobs encourage this degree as it gives a high sense of natural mindfulness of the world around you. Jobs for Forestry majors include conservation, land management and environmental science.
 Employment opportunities right now are with the following companies and organizations:
*Mitigation Management - Environmental Scientist II
*Student Conservation Association - Integrated Fire and Recreation (Internship)
*That's it for Athens...jobs are a little light right now.